        "content": " quality of output.\n*   **Hardware Optimization:** You can optimize the model to run specifically on your local GPU or N",
        "timestamp": "2026-04-14T05:29:16.645Z"
      },
      {
        "content": "PU architecture.\n\n### 6. Ethical and Transparent Operations\nAs per the governance of **ZombieCoder**, local-first AI promotes",
